<br />
<h2>Book your perfect holiday to Lake Garda today.</h2>
<br />
<p>The rich history, perfect Mediterranean climate and character of harbour towns and hillside villages provide a feast for the senses. <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> with its crystal clear waters, coves and beaches is perfect for swimming, sailing or windsurfing, you can hire a boat or let someone else do the hard work and take a boat trip, while a network of ferries provide the best transportation for exploring nearby towns and points of interest.</p>
<p>Save an extra £100 per couple, on top of our existing deals for May departures on selected Lake Garda holidays*.</p>
<h3>Hurry! Lake Garda flash sale must end Monday 8th April.</h3>
<p> </p>
